## ✖ dplyr::filter() masks stats::filter()
## ✖ dplyr::lag()    masks stats::lag()
load("datos_completos.RData")
desm_fiscal2017 <- desm_fiscal2017 %>% 
  mutate(Código = str_pad(Código, 5, "left", "0"))
icfes2018_2_w <- icfes2018_2 %>% 
  mutate(ESTU_COD_RESIDE_MCPIO = str_pad(ESTU_COD_RESIDE_MCPIO, 5, "left", "0"),
         edad = as.numeric(as.Date("2018/08/12") - 
                           as.Date(ESTU_FECHANACIMIENTO, "%d/%m/%Y"))/365,
         edad_ac = floor(edad)) %>% 
  filter(edad >= 17 & edad <= 22)
resumICFES <- icfes2018_2_w %>% 
  group_by(ESTU_COD_RESIDE_MCPIO, ESTU_MCPIO_RESIDE,
           ESTU_COD_RESIDE_DEPTO, ESTU_DEPTO_RESIDE) %>% 
  summarise(PUNT_GLOBAL = mean(PUNT_GLOBAL, na.rm = TRUE))
## Warning: Factor `ESTU_MCPIO_RESIDE` contains implicit NA, consider using
## `forcats::fct_explicit_na`
## Warning: Factor `ESTU_DEPTO_RESIDE` contains implicit NA, consider using
## `forcats::fct_explicit_na`

Comparación con el desempeño fiscal.

total <- resumICFES %>% 
  inner_join(desm_fiscal2017, by = c("ESTU_COD_RESIDE_MCPIO" = "Código"))
## Warning: Factor `ESTU_MCPIO_RESIDE` contains implicit NA, consider using
## `forcats::fct_explicit_na`
dep_mas_mun <- sort(table(total$ESTU_DEPTO_RESIDE), decreasing = TRUE)
nom_dep_mas_mun <- names(dep_mas_mun)[dep_mas_mun >= 12]
temp <- total %>% 
  filter(ESTU_DEPTO_RESIDE %in% nom_dep_mas_mun) %>% 
  mutate(ESTU_DEPTO_RESIDE = factor(ESTU_DEPTO_RESIDE,
                                    levels = nom_dep_mas_mun))

ggplot(temp, aes(Indicador.de.desempeño.Fiscal.7.,
                  PUNT_GLOBAL)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method = lm) +
  facet_wrap(~ ESTU_DEPTO_RESIDE)

Con variables demográficas y familiares.

icfes2018_2_w <- icfes2018_2_w %>% 
  select(FAMI_TIENEHORNOMICROOGAS, FAMI_PERSONASHOGAR, edad, COLE_JORNADA,
         PUNT_GLOBAL)

Con edad.

ggplot(icfes2018_2_w, aes(edad, PUNT_GLOBAL)) +
  geom_point(alpha = 0.1) +
  geom_smooth()

### Microondas.

Personas en el hogar.

Jornada del colegio

## Combinaciones

resum_icfes2018_w <- icfes2018_2_w %>% 
  group_by(FAMI_TIENEHORNOMICROOGAS, FAMI_PERSONASHOGAR, COLE_JORNADA) %>% 
  summarise(edad_prom = mean(edad, na.rm = TRUE),
            PUNT_GLOBAL_prom = mean(PUNT_GLOBAL, na.rm = TRUE))
## Warning: Factor `FAMI_TIENEHORNOMICROOGAS` contains implicit NA, consider
## using `forcats::fct_explicit_na`
## Warning: Factor `FAMI_PERSONASHOGAR` contains implicit NA, consider using
## `forcats::fct_explicit_na`
ggplot(resum_icfes2018_w, aes(edad_prom, PUNT_GLOBAL_prom, col = FAMI_TIENEHORNOMICROOGAS)) +
  geom_point() +
  facet_grid(FAMI_PERSONASHOGAR ~ COLE_JORNADA) +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1))
